### Dataset Facts
- **7,831 compounds**, **12 binary toxicity endpoints**
- **NaN prevalence:** 15–25% per endpoint (use -1 sentinel, mask during loss)
- **Toxic prevalence:** 2.8% (NR-AR-LBD) → 16.9% (SR-MMP) — severe, endpoint-variable imbalance

